[[# posting]]

[[=]]
++* Posting Your Own Art
[[/=]]

If you'd like to post your own art to the site, please check out [[[how-to-post-your-art-to-the-scp-wiki |this guide first!]]] It goes over image hosting, basic CSS formatting, customization, and posting requirements. You're free to personalize the page however you like, but note that artwork and artist pages are subject to the [[[deletions-guide|Deletions process]]] like any other posted page.

